<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.8.1/css/all.css" integrity="sha384-50oBUHEmvpQ+1lW4y57PTFmhCaXp0ML5d60M1M7uH2+nqUivzIebhndOJK28anvf" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Julius+Sans+One" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Londrina+Shadow" rel="stylesheet">
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>Pocket PT</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-ggOyR0iXCbMQv3Xipma34MD+dH/1fQ784/j6cY/iJTQUOhcWr7x9JvoRxT2MZw1T" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-q8i/X+965DzO0rT7abK41JStQIAqVgRVzpbzo5smXKp4YfRvH+8abtTE1Pi6jizo" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.14.7/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-UO2eT0CpHqdSJQ6hJty5KVphtPhzWj9WO1clHTMGa3JDZwrnQq4sF86dIHNDz0W1" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-JjSmVgyd0p3pXB1rRibZUAYoIIy6OrQ6VrjIEaFf/nJGzIxFDsf4x0xIM+B07jRM" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-md  sticky-top" style="background-color: rgba(22, 22, 22, 0.7)">
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="collapse_target">
            <a class="nav-link" id="logo" href="/home"><i class="fas fa-dumbbell"> </i>Pocket PT</a>          
            <ul class="navbar-nav ml-auto" >
                <li class="nav-item btn" >
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/diets">Diets</a>                    
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item btn" >
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/exercises">Exercises</a>    
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item btn" >
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/logout">Log Out</a>                 
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>  
    <div id="homecontent" >    
        <div id="profilecontainer">
            <div id="photoname">
                <img src="<%=user.image%>" id="profileimg">
                <br/>
                <br/>
                <h5><%= user.name %></h5>
            </div>
            <br/>
            <div id="#list">           
                <p>
                    <% var inches = user.info.height; %>
                    <% var feet = Math.floor(inches / 12); %>
                    <% inches %= 12; %>
                    Age: <%= user.info.age %> <br/>
                    weight: <%= user.info.weight %>lb <br/>
                    Height: <%= feet %>'<%= inches %>" 
                </p>   
            </div>                
            <div id="calinfo">
                <p>
                    Caloric Intake: <%= calIntake %> cal <br/> Caloric Output: <%= bmr %> cal </br></br>
                    Macros Caloric Ratio: <br>
                    Carb: <%= carb %> cal <br/> Prot: <%= prot %> cal <br/> Fats: <%= fat %> cal
                </p>
            </div>
            <a href="/updateinfo">Update Info</a>
        </div>
        <div id="tips">
            
            <% if (user.info.exp == "beginner") { %> 
                
                <div class="beginertips">
                    <h1> Hello <%= user.name %></h1>
                    <h5>Beginner Tips:</h5>
                    <p>
                        <ol>
                            <li>
                                As a beginner, it is highly recommended that <br/>
                                you keep control of your repetitions.<br/>
                                The results you will get from lifting the wights <br/>
                                calmly and properly will be more important <br/>
                                than the amount of weight that you're tying to lift,<br/> 
                                don't let your ego outshine your goal!<br>
                            </li>
                            <br/>
                            <li>
                                Make fitness a Habit. It will be hard at first, <br/>
                                but following the plan is the best way to keep it simple.<br/>
                                Your Workout plan consists of a 3 day/week resistance <br/>
                                trainnig routine, which will allow you to have proper<br/> 
                                rest between workouts.
                            </li>
                            <br/>
                            <li>
                                Diet like you mean it. The biggest bridge between where <br/>
                                you are now and your goal, is your eating habits.<br/>
                                Pocket PT gives you suggetions for 5 meals/day from 3 different <br/>
                                diet styles, which will make your life much easier<br/>
                                Eating the same meals everyday makes you transform your diet <br/>
                                into a routine, giving you the consistency you need. 
                            </li>
                        </ol>
                        <br/>
                        " Pain is the weakness leaving the body. . . "<br/>
                          Arnold Schwarzenegger.    
                    </p>
                </div>
                <% } %>
                
                <% if (user.info.exp == "intermediate") { %>
                <h5>Intermediate Tips:</h5>
                <p>
                    
                </p>
            <% } %>
            
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>